"function decode_place_spec(jobj)
    xs = jobj["xs"]
    ys = jobj["ys"]
    as = jobj["as"]
    ws = jobj["ws"]
    hs = jobj["hs"]
    Es = jobj["Es"]
    mask = jobj["mask"]
    diearea = jobj["diearea"]
    params = jobj["place-params"]
    xs, ys, as, ws, hs, Es, mask, diearea, params
end"
